        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">The PV is expressed in kg. The PV in an underestimation of the actual market production volume, since it is based on its solely production as battery electrolyte additive.  

According to UN Comtrade (https://comtrade.un.org/data/, HS code: 850760) 191922359 kg Li-ion batteries were exported from China in 2019. Electrolyte makes on average 0.3% weight of a Li-ion battery pack. 
</productionVolumeComment>
