      <intermediateExchange id="436317f9-c144-5eb3-8500-fe83e07b31bf" unitId="77ae64fa-7e74-4252-9c3b-889c1cd20bfc" amount="0.399063145089249" intermediateExchangeId="759b89bd-3aa6-42ad-b767-5bb9ef5d331d" activityLinkId="2a362a40-b1c0-591a-8bb3-b9d6ab94a192">
        <name xml:lang="en">electricity, medium voltage</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kWh</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on literature data published by the GENDORF Chemical Park. The factory produced an average of 2462760 tonnes of chemical substances (including intermediates) per year in the years 2015-2019. The average consumption of electricity in the years 2015-2019 was 982796751 kWh per year. This equals 0.39906 kWh/kg chemical produced.

References:
Chemiepark GENDORF, Umwelterklärung 2016, https://www.gendorf.de/Nachbarn/Umweltschutz/Industrie%20und%20Nachhaltigkeit
